data.description: Welcome to 729 Grand Valley in Maumee!! Nestled in a quiet and secluded neighborhood not far from the river, this beautiful home has so much room for entertaining and so many NEW upgrades within the last 5 years including new flooring throughout the first floor, new countertops, painted cabinets, new refrigerator & oven, newer furnace, new deck, new water heater, new sump pump, new flooring in basement, shiplap accent walls- there is truly nothing to do but move in! Enjoy being near all of the best restaurants, bars, shops, & parks Maumee has to offer!
